    "More specific examples are provided in Supplementary Fig. 1d.",
    "The SOTA model for this dataset is reported as the MatBERT-based model whose F1 scores for DES and MOR are 0.67 and 0.92, respectively 8.",
    "Instead of adopting fine-tuning, we used the few-shot learning 47 of the GPT-3.5 model ('text-davinci-003') for the AuNPs entities dataset, as there are not sufficient datasets (N = 85).",
    "Similar to the previous NER task, we designed three prompts such as random retrieval, task-informed random retrieval and kNN retrieval (Fig. 4 and Supplementary Table 2).",
    "First, we randomly select the three ground-truth examples (i.e., pair of text and the text with named entities) from the original training and validation set when extracting the named entities from the given text in the test set (random retrieval)."
